Personal Portfolio Website

📌 Project Overview

This is my Personal Portfolio Website built using pure HTML5.

The purpose of this project is to showcase my web development learning journey, skills, projects, achievements, and future goals in a professional way.

This project was created as part of my HTML learning journey in the SMIT MERN Stack Development Program.

---

🚀 Features

- Semantic HTML5 Structure
- Professional Portfolio Layout
- Navigation Menu
- Hero Section
- About Me Section
- Education Section
- Skills Section
- Tools & Technologies
- Services Section
- Projects Showcase
- Learning Roadmap
- Achievements Section
- Gallery Section
- Contact Form
- Social Links
- Footer Section
- SEO Meta Tags
- Favicon Support

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5

